---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dean Williamson - The Glob">
	<div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto py-5 px-5">
		<!-- Quote Section -->
		<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#e8f5e8] to-[#f0f7f0] p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
			<p class="text-[1.5rem] italic text-glob-orange text-center">"When did you last service your ute, tractor, motorbike, or more importantly... self?!!!"</p>
		</div>

		<!-- The Story Section -->
		<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-[20pt] font-bold text-glob-dark mb-4">The Story Behind The Glob</h2>
			<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[1.6] text-glob-dark mb-4">Last year our company donated The Glob Rural Health Check caravan to the local regional Lions Clubs so they could carry on the free health check initiative, and set the template for other regions around New Zealand to follow.</p>

			<h3 class="text-[16pt] font-bold text-glob-dark mb-3">The Mission</h3>
			<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[1.6] text-glob-dark mb-4">The mission and message is simple:</p>
			<blockquote class="text-[1.2rem] italic text-glob-gray border-l-4 border-glob-gold pl-6 my-6">
				To prove the need for rural community people, and farmers especially, to put a regular health check for themselves at the top of their list of farm maintenance priorities.
			</blockquote>

			<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[1.6] text-glob-dark">The actual community health check screening activity with The Glob, including the enjoyable conversations it triggers and the hard data it provides, is simply a fun, visible and memorable tactic used to highlight that important message.</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Impact Section -->
		<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#e8f5e8] to-[#f0f7f0] border border-glob-gold p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-[20pt] font-bold text-glob-dark mb-4">Impact in Action</h2>
			<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[1.6] text-glob-dark mb-4">It's been great to see The Lions Clubs out and about with The Glob at sale yards and farming community events.</p>

			<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 text-center mt-6">
				<span class="text-[3rem] font-bold text-glob-orange block">20-25%</span>
				<span class="text-[1.1rem] text-glob-dark mt-4 block max-w-[500px] mx-auto">of farmers who had their checks had to be referred on to their GPs, highlighting how important it is for us all to get a regular health check.</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- About Agri HQ Section -->
		<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg">
			<h2 class="text-[20pt] font-bold text-glob-dark mb-4">About Agri HQ</h2>
			<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[1.6] text-glob-dark mb-4">Agri HQ is a media company based in Feilding that deals mainly with rural communities. In this capacity, they attend many rural events and saw the opportunity to bring health checks directly to farmers.</p>
			<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[1.6] text-glob-dark">Two years ago, they decided to set up a "My Health Check" service, purchased a caravan, and converted it into a mobile medical facility with a separate consulting room - The Glob was born.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
